      <title>泰国能源大亨在股价创纪录暴跌后面临欺诈指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/thai-energy-tycoon-faces-fraud-charges-after-record-stock-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国证券市场监管机构对 Energy Absolute Pcl 的首席执行官提出了欺诈和腐败指控，这家陷入困境的可再生能源公司上个月股价创下历史新高，导致其创始人作​​为抵押品的部分股份被强制出售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/thai-energy-tycoon-faces-fraud-charges-after-record-stock-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 04:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
